title: Barnaby and Me (1978 - Australia) charming family adventure
description:
Barnaby and Me (1978 - Australia)

Adventure / Comedy / Family
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0075728/


Filmed at Sydney, New South Wales, Australia

International con-man Leo jumps ship in Sydney. Posing as a zoologist he strikes up a relationship with Jennifer, and her koala Barnaby. On a treasure seeking adventure they stumble upon a mysterious valley where the natives worship the koala and are "extraordinarily happy." Leo discovers a money making bonanza, a special native confection which when eaten produces a happy euphoria. He decides to go into business, however their confection has a most unpleasant side effect.

In his 1982 book "Where Have I Been? An Autobiography", a sobered-up Sid Caesar admits that by the time he did this film, he was so far-gone because of his prescription drug and alcohol addiction, he has no memory of making this movie, or of even being in Australia.
